  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a single center, non randomized study to gather data to correlate physiological
      signals with the patient's fluid status during fluid removal in hemodialysis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients undergoing hemodialysis will be monitored with the study device . The collected
      information will be correlated with fluid loss.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
